01:23:04,945 --> 01:23:08,676
No problems. Grandpa's room is empty
and money's a bit tight right now

735
01:23:09,283 --> 01:23:11,251
And if you're around,
mom will love you

736
01:23:11,451 --> 01:23:13,851
Mom will love me?
- She always wanted a son like you...

737
01:23:14,354 --> 01:23:18,586
Clean. But got me instead!
You two will get along superbly

738
01:23:18,959 --> 01:23:21,757
And wait till you
taste her cooking

739
01:23:22,629 --> 01:23:26,929
Mom's cooking!
- Yeah, she has only two missions

740
01:23:27,367 --> 01:23:30,268
One, to reform me.
Two, to feed everyone

741
01:23:32,539 --> 01:23:34,507
And your dad?

742
01:23:39,646 --> 01:23:44,811
Ram, you're my friend
and all my friends know this

743
01:23:46,119 --> 01:23:48,451
Do not speak to me
about my father

744
01:23:49,389 --> 01:23:50,356
Never

745
01:24:00,934 --> 01:24:02,902
That's our home

746
01:24:03,604 --> 01:24:05,799
Lakshman,
there's no electricity...?

747
01:24:07,274 --> 01:24:12,906
I'm history! Mom had asked me
to repair the fuse

748
01:24:13,280 --> 01:24:14,907
I'll go and get
the fuse repaired buddy...

749
01:24:15,282 --> 01:24:17,250
you go and calm mom down.
- I'm coming with you...

750
01:24:17,384 --> 01:24:19,352
I'll be back in two minutes!
- No Lakshman, how will I...?

751
01:24:19,686 --> 01:24:21,244
Just two minutes!

752
01:24:23,957 --> 01:24:25,788
But how will I...? Mom...

753
01:25:05,432 --> 01:25:07,400
Are you back, son?

754
01:25:13,373 --> 01:25:15,898
What took you so long?

755
01:25:20,280 --> 01:25:22,248
And why are you so quiet?

756
01:25:23,283 --> 01:25:24,841
I knew you'd forget again

757
01:25:25,285 --> 01:25:27,810
Do you know how long I've been
in darkness? We have a blown fuse

758
01:25:28,322 --> 01:25:30,916
Forget it, I'll scold you later,
but first take the Lord's blessings

759
01:25:31,758 --> 01:25:34,921
Oh Lord, I hope
he passes this year...

760
01:25:35,595 --> 01:25:39,258
makes his mother proud
finds every joy in life

761
01:25:42,636 --> 01:25:44,604
Who...? Who are you?

762
01:25:48,775 --> 01:25:51,073
I thought it's my son...
- I...

763
01:25:52,479 --> 01:25:53,537
I'm...

764
01:25:55,916 --> 01:25:59,977
This is Ram, mom, my friend,
and your new paying guest

765
01:26:01,254 --> 01:26:03,222
Ram, this is mom

766
01:26:04,691 --> 01:26:05,953
I know

767
01:26:13,266 --> 01:26:15,234
He's just your type

768
01:26:22,275 --> 01:26:23,742
Bless you, son

769
01:26:36,842 --> 01:26:38,070
Ram...

770
01:26:40,846 --> 01:26:42,939
here, have it hot

771
01:26:43,382 --> 01:26:46,146
Enough, aunty.
I just had loads... please!

772
01:26:46,519 --> 01:26:48,000
Enough already? You're young,
you need more. Come on

1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,487
Enough already? You're young,
you need more. Come on

2
00:00:01,188 --> 00:00:03,156
I'm not as young you make me out be.
If I continue eating like this...

3
00:00:03,323 --> 00:00:06,087
I'll have a paunch in a week's time.
- Good! A little paunch is appealing

4
00:00:06,326 --> 00:00:08,294
Oh no aunty!
- It's a sign of prosperity

5
00:00:10,197 --> 00:00:12,563
I'll get one more
- No, no... absolutely not

6
00:00:13,467 --> 00:00:15,264
Why? Aren't they nice?

7
00:00:16,070 --> 00:00:19,301
It's not that aunty.
They say...

8
00:00:19,973 --> 00:00:22,066
mother's hands create magic
no matter what

9
00:00:22,876 --> 00:00:25,572
Yes. Lucky told me

10
00:00:27,881 --> 00:00:29,508
I'm sorry, son

11
00:00:31,218 --> 00:00:33,846
So, did your father bring you up?

12
00:00:34,221 --> 00:00:38,282
Yes. He nurtured me,
brought me up

13
00:00:40,494 --> 00:00:42,462
My father was... is
a really nice man

14
00:00:44,331 --> 00:00:46,458
Never let me feel
my mother's absence

15
00:00:47,534 --> 00:00:50,196
But yes, he could never
cook like this

16
00:00:51,905 --> 00:00:55,033
Actually aunty, I am what I am
because of my father

17
00:00:56,910 --> 00:01:00,038
You're very nice, Ram!
Your father must be a nice man too

18
00:01:00,447 --> 00:01:01,414
Yes

19
00:01:02,850 --> 00:01:04,818
Fathers are so important

20
00:01:09,523 --> 00:01:14,256
Sometimes I feel if
Lucky's father was with us...

21
00:01:17,197 --> 00:01:19,324
Aunty, if you don't mind my asking...

22
00:01:20,400 --> 00:01:22,834
I mean, Lucky's father...?

23
00:01:23,036 --> 00:01:24,833
We don't live together

24
00:01:25,873 --> 00:01:29,172
We had a fight and I left home

25
00:01:31,578 --> 00:01:33,546
But didn't he come
to take you back...?

26
00:01:34,414 --> 00:01:36,848
Several times

27
00:01:38,418 --> 00:01:43,185
It's been seven years now, Madhu.
Please come back now

28
00:01:45,826 --> 00:01:47,316
Haven't you forgiven me yet?

29
00:01:48,829 --> 00:01:50,797
It's not about forgiveness
any more, Shekhar

30
00:01:51,832 --> 00:01:54,460
Even if I reconcile
with your infidelity...

31
00:01:56,436 --> 00:01:59,200
I cannot bear to live
with that boy at home

32
00:01:59,540 --> 00:02:00,802
Madhu, please

33
00:02:04,611 --> 00:02:06,044
He needs me

34
00:02:06,847 --> 00:02:10,146
Just him? What about me, Shekhar?

35
00:02:12,953 --> 00:02:15,547
And is Lakshman not your son?

36
00:02:21,061 --> 00:02:23,029
You will need to choose, Shekhar

37
00:02:23,864 --> 00:02:26,094
Lakshman and I will
come with you right away

38
00:02:27,868 --> 00:02:29,836
But only if you want it this way

39
00:02:45,819 --> 00:02:48,049
Mom...
- His Highness has arrived

40
00:02:52,960 --> 00:02:55,793
Lucky, you're a walking mess!
- Where are my shoes, mom?

41
00:02:55,996 --> 00:02:59,397
Why don't you cut your hair?
And why're you a wearing doggy leash?

42
00:02:59,900 --> 00:03:03,802
Your jeans are torn!
And your shirt... son, give it to me!

43
00:03:04,137 --> 00:03:06,002
I'll stitch it up in two minutes!
- Torn...?

44
00:03:06,273 --> 00:03:08,400
I sat up since morning with a blade
to get it this way and you say...

45
00:03:08,609 --> 00:03:11,100
Mom, it's fashion!
- Don't call me 'mom', Lakshman!

46
00:03:11,845 --> 00:03:16,407
Then don't call me 'Lakshman', mom!
Lakshman - I hate the name Lakshman!

47
00:03:16,850 --> 00:03:19,318
Why? It's a lovely name.
Lakshman Prasad

48
00:03:19,920 --> 00:03:22,411
And goes well with your image.
- Oh, don't you just love it?

49
00:03:22,856 --> 00:03:25,222
Ram-Lakshman, seems like Mahabharat
started in this very house!

50
00:03:26,860 --> 00:03:29,294
The Ramayan!
- Whatever! I'm off

51
00:03:29,930 --> 00:03:31,522
Lakshman, you won't be able
to get up tomorrow as well

52
00:03:31,865 --> 00:03:33,389
I will mom...
- Tomorrow's Tuesday

53
00:03:33,567 --> 00:03:35,535
I have to go to the temple.
- And we will, mom

54
00:03:35,869 --> 00:03:37,928
I know you won't wake up.
- Temples are so boring, mom

55
00:03:38,138 --> 00:03:39,105
Ok, Ok, Ok!

56
00:03:39,339 --> 00:03:41,773
I'll take mother... I mean aunty,
to the temple

57
00:03:42,809 --> 00:03:46,267
Ram, you're godsend!
See, problem solved

58
00:03:58,592 --> 00:04:03,461
May I call you 'mother'?
- Only if you eat my food every day

59
00:04:04,831 --> 00:04:06,458
Then forget it, aunty

60
00:04:07,034 --> 00:04:08,228
Bye mom!

61
00:04:08,602 --> 00:04:11,298
He'll come back late in the night.
This boy hardly sleeps

62
00:04:14,895 --> 00:04:17,455
Wake up. Wake up, you morons!

63
00:04:18,899 --> 00:04:23,268
I had given you an assignment
on Physics 3 days back...

64
00:04:24,171 --> 00:04:26,139
Heat and Pressure

65
00:04:29,910 --> 00:04:33,107
And I would be delighted
if someone has not done it

66
00:04:33,314 --> 00:04:34,872
Why sir?
- Because...

67
00:04:35,349 --> 00:04:38,477
then you'll have to do
the same assignment five times

68
00:04:43,657 --> 00:04:45,488
Why does he spit?
- Take out your homework

69
00:04:45,860 --> 00:04:47,828
You too... you too...

70
00:04:48,229 --> 00:04:50,390
And ah! Lucky!

71
00:04:51,198 --> 00:04:52,130
Lucky!!

72
00:04:55,536 --> 00:04:57,003
Homework?
- I have it

73
00:04:57,204 --> 00:04:59,331
Trying to con me, eh?
- No, sir

74
00:04:59,874 --> 00:05:02,502
Today we'll separate the wheat
from the chaff

75
00:05:02,877 --> 00:05:03,844
One second, sir!

76
00:05:03,944 --> 00:05:05,912
Yes, do search below as well.
Maybe you dropped it there

77
00:05:06,113 --> 00:05:09,844
But if it's not there
I suggest you start praying...

78
00:05:10,284 --> 00:05:14,243
as only Lord Ram can
save you today

79
00:05:18,492 --> 00:05:20,517
I know that your homework...

80
00:05:22,496 --> 00:05:24,191
is done!

81
00:05:24,899 --> 00:05:26,059
I don't believe it!

82
00:05:31,972 --> 00:05:35,874
And have you done your home work?

83
00:05:37,011 --> 00:05:38,137
No, sir!

84
00:05:39,914 --> 00:05:40,881
Got you!

85
00:05:51,859 --> 00:05:54,384
I miss the army. I've to get down on
my knees at the drop of a spit-ball!

86
00:05:55,296 --> 00:05:57,491
If anyone sees me here,
I'd definitely be court martialled!

87
00:06:24,892 --> 00:06:26,189
You?

88
00:06:27,094 --> 00:06:28,857
You're up to something again?
- No ma'am!

89
00:06:29,130 --> 00:06:31,860
I'm going to have you expelled!
- No Ma'am, I wasn't singing

90
00:06:33,000 --> 00:06:34,968
Then what?
Why are you on your knees?

91
00:06:35,503 --> 00:06:40,805
I've been...
punished by Mr Rasai!

92
00:06:41,842 --> 00:06:43,309
Really?
- Really

93
00:06:46,847 --> 00:06:48,474
I know it is very silly

94
00:06:52,019 --> 00:06:56,422
"Oh lord! This boy
is nutty as a pie..."

95
00:06:57,191 --> 00:07:01,150
"why is it so hard
to make him realize..."

96
00:07:01,529 --> 00:07:05,829
"that first the heart pines,
but slowly..."

97
00:07:06,867 --> 00:07:10,564
"and only on the way one finds love,
then you fall freely"

98
00:07:18,913 --> 00:07:21,438
Rohan, have you seen Lucky?
- He's in the library

99
00:07:21,916 --> 00:07:22,905
Library?

100
00:08:17,871 --> 00:08:19,338
You're Lucky, right?

101
00:08:19,873 --> 00:08:22,171
Why don't you go and put it up
on the college notice board?

102
00:08:27,448 --> 00:08:31,009
You're Sanju's boyfriend, right?
- Hey double battery, single power!

103
00:08:31,619 --> 00:08:34,019
Sanju? My girlfriend?
Are you mad?

104
00:08:34,588 --> 00:08:37,955
Lucky's girlfriend will be
the world's most beautiful girl

105
00:08:38,392 --> 00:08:41,793
Not a plain Jane like Sanju.
Now buzz off

106
00:08:42,296 --> 00:08:44,127
I have to study

107
00:09:03,651 --> 00:09:06,484
My dad is not dead, Ram

108
00:09:07,855 --> 00:09:09,482
I know

109
00:09:17,865 --> 00:09:20,493
He never loved me

110
00:09:23,871 --> 00:09:25,839
He always wanted a son...

111
00:09:27,875 --> 00:09:31,242
who would make him proud,
join the army like him

112
00:09:37,885 --> 00:09:42,185
Are sons everything?
And daughters mean nothing?

113
00:09:45,492 --> 00:09:46,459
Sanju...

114
00:09:53,901 --> 00:09:56,870
Even as a child I tried to be
my father's 'son'

115
00:09:59,907 --> 00:10:01,875
And look, I've succeeded

116
00:10:03,977 --> 00:10:06,207
No one even remembers
that I'm a girl

117
00:10:08,716 --> 00:10:12,880
Sanju, you're fine the way you are

118
00:10:16,223 --> 00:10:19,454
It's time we remind everyone that
you're the most beautiful girl...

119
00:10:21,061 --> 00:10:23,029
not only in the college,
but the world

120
00:10:24,264 --> 00:10:27,233
Come with me.
- No Ram, please

121
00:10:31,939 --> 00:10:32,906
I'm here now

122
00:10:36,944 --> 00:10:40,380
Yes Ram!!
- Good evening ma'am!

123
00:10:40,881 --> 00:10:42,849
Can you make me
look exactly like you?

124
00:10:43,884 --> 00:10:48,844
What???
- Yes... not me. Sanju

125
00:10:54,194 --> 00:10:56,526
Hi Sanju!
- Hello ma'am!

126
00:10:56,964 --> 00:10:59,933
Come on... Come, come!

127
00:11:03,237 --> 00:11:05,205
See you Ram!
- When?

128
00:11:20,921 --> 00:11:22,889
Physics assignment. Five times!

129
00:11:24,625 --> 00:11:29,585
You did my physics assignment?
And five times? I don't believe it

130
00:11:30,464 --> 00:11:33,558
I thought I'll do it thrice
but by the third time...

131
00:11:33,934 --> 00:11:36,232
it actually started to make sense,
so I decided to the rest as well

132
00:11:37,271 --> 00:11:39,034
By the way, you're welcome!

133
00:11:39,940 --> 00:11:44,400
Oh, thank you!
I was about to say thank you!

134
00:11:45,212 --> 00:11:48,841
I said, you're welcome. Just do me
a favour, don't tell anyone

135
00:11:49,249 --> 00:11:52,218
I got a reputation to protect.
- Of course. School, Lucky and all

136
00:11:53,954 --> 00:11:56,855
Actually, you can
tell Sanju about it

137
00:11:58,258 --> 00:12:02,285
She keeps chewing brains. This will
shut her up for at least two weeks

138
00:12:02,896 --> 00:12:04,557
You know what I mean...
- Yeah, I know what you mean!

139
00:12:04,898 --> 00:12:07,025
You mean you like Sanju a lot
- Like...?

140
00:12:07,301 --> 00:12:10,099
Yes. Like.
- As in...?

141
00:12:10,304 --> 00:12:13,273
As in... you know as in...

142
00:12:14,374 --> 00:12:16,535
You are crazy man!
- No, no! You are crazy about Sanju!

143
00:12:16,910 --> 00:12:18,878
No, no! You are crazy!
- No, you are crazy about crazy Sanju!

144
00:12:19,112 --> 00:12:24,209
Ram, when Lucky will fall in love
the entire college will hear violins

145
00:12:27,921 --> 00:12:29,548
Sanju? No

146
00:12:33,927 --> 00:12:36,225
Sanju... no way, Ram

147
00:13:08,996 --> 00:13:10,588
Shut your mouth, uncle

148
00:13:19,907 --> 00:13:23,468
"Love is such a tornado,
Love is such a storm"

149
00:13:24,044 --> 00:13:27,878
"Love takes away the power
of every life form"

150
00:13:28,348 --> 00:13:32,307
"Everyone in love is crazed,
anyone in love is in a daze"

151
00:13:32,619 --> 00:13:36,282
"Love makes it all so difficult,
yet it's all so easy in love"

152
00:13:36,723 --> 00:13:38,418
"Look at these visions, these
lovesick souls, these smoking coals"

153
00:13:38,859 --> 00:13:40,827
"Look at the follies of love"

154
00:13:41,562 --> 00:13:46,158
"The woes of my heart
having glimpsed you..."

155
00:13:46,633 --> 00:13:50,000
"It's like a magical spell,
what can I say"

156
00:13:50,671 --> 00:13:54,505
"The woes of my heart
having glimpsed you..."

157
00:13:55,142 --> 00:13:58,839
"It's like a magical spell,
what can I say"

158
00:14:42,556 --> 00:14:45,184
Check that! Like that!

159
00:14:45,859 --> 00:14:50,091
"The heart is but a traveller,
and you are the oasis it seeks"

160
00:14:50,497 --> 00:14:54,126
"The heart is but a canoe,
and you are its bank with mystique"

161
00:14:54,434 --> 00:14:58,393
"What more can the heart desire,
if it has you"

162
00:14:59,039 --> 00:15:00,939
"My heart is
a Ionely place, my dear"

163
00:15:01,141 --> 00:15:02,904
"Come, I need your light
and your sparkly cheer"

164
00:15:03,910 --> 00:15:06,845
Check that! Like that!

165
00:15:07,547 --> 00:15:11,244
"Love brings all the joy,
Love has the power to destroy"

166
00:15:11,885 --> 00:15:15,514
"It is its own limitation,
but frees one like the sky"

167
00:15:16,256 --> 00:15:19,851
"In the Land of Love,
live millions of dreams each day"

168
00:15:20,560 --> 00:15:23,859
"Lucky are those who get lost,
for love has shown them the way"

169
00:15:24,364 --> 00:15:26,525
"Look at these visions pal, these
lovesick souls, these hopeful ghouls"

170
00:15:26,900 --> 00:15:28,868
"Look at the follies of love"

171
00:16:12,145 --> 00:16:14,841
Check that! Like that!

172
00:16:23,623 --> 00:16:26,183
"I worship you"

173
00:16:26,893 --> 00:16:33,856
"You are my prayer"

174
00:16:35,235 --> 00:16:37,430
"If I have loved..."

175
00:16:37,904 --> 00:16:44,207
"I have loved only this way"

176
00:16:45,245 --> 00:16:47,805
"If I have loved..."

177
00:16:48,181 --> 00:16:54,142
"I have loved
only this way"

178
00:16:56,022 --> 00:16:58,991
Check that! Wicked!!

179
00:16:59,359 --> 00:17:03,318
"My heart is going insane,
you are its only balm"

180
00:17:03,864 --> 00:17:07,493
"Why is my heart all aflutter?
Tell me, love, what is the matter"

181
00:17:08,068 --> 00:17:12,027
"Let your perfume
waft over and find me"

182
00:17:12,372 --> 00:17:16,172
"Let your hair rain
their dark clouds over me"

183
00:17:16,676 --> 00:17:19,907
Check that! Like that!

184
00:17:20,881 --> 00:17:24,612
"Sweetheart, I have
crossed the beyond..."

185
00:17:25,152 --> 00:17:29,020
"Sweetheart, you and
only you are my dawn..."

186
00:17:29,356 --> 00:17:33,315
"Sweetheart, alas. You can't see
what's in my heart"

187
00:17:33,894 --> 00:17:37,295
"Sweetheart, you'll remember me
only when I fall apart"

188
00:17:37,898 --> 00:17:39,798
"Look at these visions pal, these
lovesick souls, these hopeful ghouls"

189
00:17:40,000 --> 00:17:41,968
"Look at the follies of love"

190
00:17:43,303 --> 00:17:47,205
"The woes of my heart
having glimpsed you..."

191
00:17:47,841 --> 00:17:51,140
"It's like a magical spell,
what can I say"

192
00:17:51,511 --> 00:17:55,470
"The woes of my heart
having glimpsed you..."

193
00:17:56,183 --> 00:17:59,812
"It's like a magical spell,
what can I say"

194
00:18:17,270 --> 00:18:18,237
Hi Sanju!

195
00:18:18,872 --> 00:18:21,170
Ma'am, it worked!
- I can see that

196
00:18:21,374 --> 00:18:23,842
You're looking very pretty!
- Ma'am it's all because of you!

197
00:18:24,211 --> 00:18:25,838
Thank you so much!
- You're welcome!

198
00:18:26,046 --> 00:18:28,276
But you should thank
someone else for this

199
00:18:33,954 --> 00:18:35,854
Ma'am, isn't he different?

200
00:18:36,156 --> 00:18:37,953
Do you know he's actually older
than you are?

201
00:18:39,893 --> 00:18:43,226
I do. But he's still my student

