Major Ram... Major Ram!

728
01:08:16,370 --> 01:08:19,271
Hey shut up. Major Ram is dead!

729
01:08:19,673 --> 01:08:21,641
They killed Major Ram!
Murderers!

730
01:08:22,343 --> 01:08:25,642
You are a very bad man.
- Shut up and sit there!

731
01:08:26,781 --> 01:08:28,612
Captain Roy, go check outside

732
01:08:37,024 --> 01:08:38,491
There's no one outside

733
01:08:41,328 --> 01:08:42,295
Sit quietly

734
01:08:42,730 --> 01:08:44,891
Captain Mahesh,
there's no one there

735
01:09:27,308 --> 01:09:28,275
Let go!

736
01:09:39,420 --> 01:09:40,887
Calling all stations.

737
01:09:41,322 --> 01:09:44,291
Come in. Rai... Rai...
Mahesh

738
01:09:46,327 --> 01:09:47,521
What the hell!

739
01:09:57,671 --> 01:09:59,866
What about you?
- Please, please... go away please go

740
01:10:00,341 --> 01:10:01,968
Move it! Go

741
01:10:08,415 --> 01:10:11,316
I have to do something for father.
Please go!

742
01:10:13,053 --> 01:10:14,020
Go

743
01:10:49,657 --> 01:10:51,625
Go. Find him now.
Quick

744
01:10:52,359 --> 01:10:57,296
Why did you do this Khan?
Why did you deceive me?

745
01:10:58,332 --> 01:11:01,631
No, it was you who
deceived us, Raghavan

746
01:11:03,037 --> 01:11:06,006
I supported you for our country...

747
01:11:07,441 --> 01:11:09,875
not to avenge your son.
- Khan!

748
01:11:11,345 --> 01:11:15,782
It's not a personal war, Raghavan.
It's not a personal war damn it!

749
01:11:16,350 --> 01:11:20,309
It always is, Khan. It always is

750
01:11:42,309 --> 01:11:44,800
Ram... Ram

751
01:11:46,013 --> 01:11:47,981
What happen?
- I saw them escape, Commander

752
01:11:48,315 --> 01:11:51,284
I was fixing explosives on the roof.
- Major Ram can't escape!

753
01:11:52,386 --> 01:11:53,978
Go find him damn it!

754
01:11:57,925 --> 01:11:59,893
You won't come out
like this, Ram

755
01:12:09,403 --> 01:12:10,961
