758
01:12:15,943 --> 01:12:17,911
Sanju, he's my brother

759
01:12:19,346 --> 01:12:21,906
Don't go... please.
- He's my brother

760
01:12:25,319 --> 01:12:27,787
Ram... Ram

761
01:12:32,359 --> 01:12:35,726
Why scream? If you call from
your heart, you will even find God

762
01:12:37,798 --> 01:12:41,598
The sun is rising. No one can stop
Project Milaap now. Not even you

763
01:12:43,971 --> 01:12:46,269
In five minutes the army will be here
to arrest you, Raghavan

764
01:12:48,309 --> 01:12:50,277
You have truly lost

765
01:12:50,711 --> 01:12:53,942
I'm the one with the gun, Ram.
How can I lose?

766
01:12:55,416 --> 01:12:59,978
I can finish you off in a second and
parcel you to your father if I wish

767
01:13:01,522 --> 01:13:06,960
But, I'm sure he can wait
another five minutes

768
01:13:10,331 --> 01:13:11,958
Five minutes, Ram

769
01:15:08,782 --> 01:15:10,340
Hurry up, Captain!

770
